        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-5 mx-auto mb-4">
          <!-- Content -->
          <h6 class="fw-bold mb-4">
            ABOUT
          </h6>
          <p>
            Hello I am Pierce Connaughton and this is my first Ruby On Rails website. 
            The website allows you to create posts on the website that other users can like and comment on.
            You can also choose to follow other users on the site displaying there posts on your feed first.
            I used PostgreSQL for the database and Action Storage to store the images that the users upload.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Grid column -->
        <div class="col-md-3 col-lg-2 col-xl-2 mx-auto mb-4">
          <!-- Links -->
          <h6 class="text-uppercase fw-bold mb-4">
            Quick links
          </h6>
          <% if account_signed_in? %>
          <p>
            <%= link_to "Dashboard", posts_index_path, class: "text-light" %>
          </p>
           <p>
            <%= link_to "My Profile", profile_show_path(username: current_account.username), class: "text-light" %>
          </p>
          <p>
            <%= link_to "New Post", new_post_path, class: "text-light" %>
          </p>
           <p>
